OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be a mixture of some
OL,6,Fbright intervals and scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, some possibly accompanied by
OL,8,Fhail and thunder. Winds will be light
OL,9,Fand variiable.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThere will be a few light
OL,12,Fshowers around this evening, and teh
OL,13,Ffirst half of the night will be mainly
OL,14,Fdry.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FA dull wet start.
OL,17,FBrightening somewhat during the
OL,18,Fmorning but further heavy showers soon
OL,19,Fpushing in.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
